;重写pclogo时代的设置数组指令
;命令版本号v1.2

to hair.old.aset :a :v :c
hair.detect
if or (and list? :v 1=count :v) (and (not word? :a) (not array? :a)) [hair.debug.error "设置数组语法错误 stop]
if word? :a [make "a thing :a]
ifelse list? :v [mdsetitem map [? + 1] :v :a :c][setitem :v+1 :a :c]
end
bury "hair.old.aset
